-- Marriott International Plans to Open 100 Hotels in India in Next 5 Years
-- B y   A n o o p   A g r a w a l
-- 2010-11-11T05:52:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-11/marriott-international-plans-to-open-100-hotels-in-india-in-next-5-years.html
Marriott International Inc. plans to
open 100 hotels in India by 2015, according to a statement from
the hotel operator today. The hotel chain owner also plans to
start the Ritz-Carlton brand in India.  To contact the reporter on this story:
